*[[Telugu]]: [[దీపం]] (deepam), [[దివ్వె]] (divve)
{{bottom}}

===Verb===
'''to lamp'''

# {{slang}} to [[hit]], [[clout]], [[belt]], [[wallop]]
# to hunt at night using a lamp; see [[lamping]]
# {{slang}} to hang out or chill; to do nothing in particular

